articles.description: Members of the Michigan State faculty voted 61-4 to express no confidence in the eight-member governing body at the university. Meanwhile, the institution's interim president wrote to the campus community about cooperation with ongoing investigations.
articles.headline: Michigan State faculty delivers no-confidence vote on board of trustees

images.caption: The Michigan State faculty's vote against the board of trustees came largely in response to the board's decision to name John Engler the school's interim president.
images.name: John Engler [600x400] - Copy (2)

images.caption: Michigan State students, including one who jumped onto and sat on the middle of a table, interrupt an MSU board of trustees meeting to protest the school's selection of John Engler as the interim president.
images.name: MSU students vent frustration over interim president selection

videos.description: Xavier's Sean O'Mara comes off the pick-and-roll and slams down a posterizing dunk while being fouled.
videos.headline: O'Mara rocks the rim plus the foul

tracking.trackingName: NCB One-Play (O'Mara rocks the rim plus the foul) 2018/2/6 ESHEET

videos.description: Butler storms all the way back to take their first lead of the game since being up 9-8 after Sean McDermott nails a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McDermott 3 brings Butler back from 18-point deficit

videos.description: Butler continues its hot shooting in the 2nd half against Xavier as Kelan Martin hits back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Martin hits back-to-back 3s to put Butler ahead

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett sinks a pull-up 3-pointer in the final 2 minutes to give Xavier a comfortable lead.
videos.headline: Bluiett hits clutch 3

videos.description: Sean McDermott hits tough 3-pointer during final minute of play to lower Xavier's lead to 1.
videos.headline: McDermott pulls Butler within 1 late

videos.description: Butler's Kamar Baldwin splashes a 3 with under 20 seconds left to play to tie the game at 84-84.
videos.headline: Baldwin sends it to OT

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett adds to Xavier's lead in overtime with a long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bluiett drains a deep 3 in OT
